	(2978,18,'shana','shana.zou@gmail.com','','123.147.184.75','2010-12-14 10:27:24','2010-12-14 14:27:24','Hi, I have a question why point and pixel units are not necessarily best suited for web documents? Is they can\'t be changed in IE?  I should be very grateful if I can receive you answer. Thanks.',0,'1','','',0,0),
