	(2980,18,'Constraint Aids in Design | Kyle Schaeffer - Interactive Media Design','','https://kyleschaeffer.com/best-practices/constraint-aids-in-design/','69.89.31.111','2010-12-16 23:57:09','2010-12-17 03:57:09','[...] working with me? Get in touch.  Contact Me The Latestpx versus pt &laquo; Rubenstp&#039;s Design on CSS Font-Size: em vs. px vs. pt vs. percentshana on CSS Font-Size: em vs. px vs. pt vs. percentShaz on WP Tabify: Transform a SharePoint Web [...]',0,'1','','pingback',0,0),
