	(3064,18,'DF','leave@reply.com','','123.21.182.254','2012-01-04 23:59:05','2012-01-05 04:59:05','It\'s all about simple Math. Awesome. Any recommendation about line-height here? \nI use the % on the font-size in body, then ems for font-size and margins and %s for line-height for all other tags.',0,'1','','',2989,0),
