	(3189,31,'A Whole New Web? / Kyle Schaeffer\'s Web Design Blog','','http://www.kyleschaeffer.com/best-practices/a-whole-new-web/','72.167.95.134','2009-06-25 12:17:44','2009-06-25 17:17:44','[...] not saying we should do away with rounded corner techniques entirely. In fact, I use my own Karate Corners all the time, but I do it when it&#8217;s necessary and appropriate.  If I&#8217;m working on my [...]',0,'1','','pingback',0,0),
