	(3238,31,'Griffen','griffentate@live.com','http://www.squidoo.com/how-to-make-websites','75.172.101.109','2011-08-25 16:08:29','2011-08-25 21:08:29','What I would use is one div and this CSS code\n<code>#div {border-radius:10px 10px 10px 10px;-moz-border-radius:10px;-webkit-border-radius:1opx;background-color:lightgrey;}</code> and you pretty much get the same thing without any images or extra divs. Hope I helped anyone!',0,'1','','',0,0),
