	(3254,54,'Tom','koford@gmail.com','http://---','195.1.201.178','2010-03-02 08:10:02','2010-03-02 13:10:02','By using  isn\'t ment to use for \"design\" it was never ment to.\n is a tabular data, and that\'s it.\n\nBut in old days they used  to \"design\" their page\'s.\nGood bless  and CSS.',0,'1','','',0,0),
