	(3353,142,'Cesar Castro','admin@satirarpg.com','http://satirarpg.com','200.14.232.98','2010-08-30 11:47:56','2010-08-30 15:47:56','Hi,\n\nGreat tutorial, by the way I would like to know if there is some kind of search engine penalty for hiding the text of the link.\n\nThanks,',0,'1','','',0,0),
