	(3534,142,'Traffic Lights Vectors','','http://www.estetica-design-forum.com/illustration-graphic-design/43822-traffic-lights-vectors.html#post309888','82.71.204.13','2012-07-18 13:50:56','2012-07-18 17:50:56','[...] And also, here&#039;s a tutorial on how you create a hover effect on an image: https://kyleschaeffer.com/best-practi...s-image-hover/  As I mentioned, it depends on what you need it for, I can elaborate further on both matters. Also, [...]',0,'1','','pingback',0,0),
