	(3638,333,'Tom','koford@gmail.com','http://---','195.1.201.178','2010-03-02 08:17:01','2010-03-02 13:17:01','About IEtester.. great, but I\'ll wait until it stable.. so for now, I\'ll open all browerser to see if all view the same.\nAnd yea, I know.. the hard way :-(\nSometimes I discover some few and just \"google\" to find a solution, often it works.',0,'1','','',0,0),
