	(3756,538,'Musta','baltaran@gmail.com','http://www.bahassi.com','81.202.167.43','2010-07-19 07:22:50','2010-07-19 11:22:50','This is a very good start for those who are new  to ajax via jquery. I have a suggestion though while you tend to reuse this script I think it would be better to set the type of  server request , the url and the error function as global variables and method to avoid rewriting the same stuff  in every ajax call that might add.\nVery nice though and thanx',0,'1','','',0,0),
