	(3807,565,'Kyle','kylersc@gmail.com','https://kyleschaeffer.com','174.66.14.197','2011-06-14 20:07:06','2011-06-15 01:07:06','For all of you who might be having issues with this script, definitely keep an eye on the new <strong>placeholder</strong> feature of HTML5.  There is a good cross-browser implementation of this script here:  http://www.hagenburger.net/BLOG/HTML5-Input-Placeholder-Fix-With-jQuery.html',0,'1','','',0,1),
