	(3841,651,'Kyle','kylersc@gmail.com','','68.229.126.69','2010-11-19 16:27:03','2010-11-19 20:27:03','Hi, Neel.  You need to surround your web part zone (where you want the tabs to appear) in a DIV tag.  You can add a CSS class to the DIV tag (for example, <strong>class=&quot;neel-tabs&quot;</strong>), and then use that class when you\'re running my script.\n\n$(\'<strong style=\"color: red;\">.neel-tabs</strong>\').wpTabify();',0,'1','','',0,1),
