	(3963,717,'Diana','dianatennant@gmail.com','','69.46.96.183','2011-10-27 17:31:32','2011-10-27 21:31:32','Thanks - I believe this solution is being used in the site I\'m maintaining, however, we are having problems in FireFox when a dialog is opened.  The height of the dialog is the same the height of the ribbon, so that scrolling doesn\'t show the body of the dialog.  Any idea how to fix?',0,'1','','',0,0),
	(3964,717,'Timo','ich-bin@timo-klein.net','','129.35.201.173','2011-11-24 09:00:50','2011-11-24 14:00:50','It\'s nice to work something out. But I think it\'s a bit too much work for the solution.\nThe Scrolling isnt the main Problem imho, why dont just overwrite the Style?\nCheers',0,'1','','',0,0),
	(3965,717,'gopi krishna','gopi.krishna@live.in','','61.12.111.34','2011-12-01 11:38:56','2011-12-01 16:38:56','I was also facing the same issue with the starting position of the page.  In the style within  body #s4-ribbonrow  removed position: fixed;\nand now it is coming properly.',0,'1','','',3933,0),
