	(3979,717,'Syed','shadilatif@yahoo.co.uk','','193.113.57.165','2012-03-27 10:08:49','2012-03-27 14:08:49','Thanks Kyle - this worked perfect :-)\n\n@ Rod: I had a similar issue with the ribbon being center aligned on IE7 but fine on all other browsers.  To fix this I simply added \'left: 0;\' to body #s4-ribbonrow.  Hope this helps.  (eg: body #s4-ribbonrow {position: fixed; z-index: 1000; left: 0;})',0,'1','','',0,0),
