	(4070,938,'Kyle','kylersc@gmail.com','https://kyleschaeffer.com','174.66.14.197','2011-06-23 07:57:59','2011-06-23 12:57:59','Hi, Andy.  I\'m using SketchBook Pro, Photoshop CS5, and SharePoint Designer 2010.  There is actually a free version of SketchBook available on the Mac app store, so there\'s probably one you can find for Windows as well.  It\'s great for sketching out ideas and putting things quickly down in electronic format (especially if you have a pen & tablet to assist).',0,'1','','',4069,1),
