	(18490,18,'PHILL','philluk@yahoo.com','','77.103.54.11','2016-04-14 04:43:27','2016-04-14 08:43:27','People should be using rem not em for font as em inherits sizes from its parent and root em uses the base size. All modern browsers support rem.',0,'1','Mozilla/5.0 (X11; Linux x86_64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/49.0.2623.110 Safari/537.36','',0,0),
