	(24784,18,'rem、px、em之间的区别以及网页响应式设计写法 | Codeba','','http://www.codeba.cc/rem%e3%80%81px%e3%80%81em%e4%b9%8b%e9%97%b4%e7%9a%84%e5%8c%ba%e5%88%ab%e4%bb%a5%e5%8f%8a%e7%bd%91%e9%a1%b5%e5%93%8d%e5%ba%94%e5%bc%8f%e8%ae%be%e8%ae%a1%e5%86%99%e6%b3%95.html','133.130.121.67','2016-12-14 19:28:13','2016-12-15 00:28:13','[&#8230;] 在Web中使用什么单位来定义页面的字体大小，至今天为止都还在激烈的争论着，有人说PX做为单位好，有人说EM优点多，还有人在说百分比方便，以至于出现了CSS Font-Size: em vs. px vs. pt vs. percent这样的PK大局。不幸的是，仍然有不同的利弊，使各种技术都不太理想，但又无法不去用。真是进也难，退也难呀。 [&#8230;]',0,'0','The Incutio XML-RPC PHP Library -- WordPress/4.5.4','pingback',0,0),
	(24938,18,'Webtady','social@webtady.com','https://www.webtady.com/professional-small-business-web-design-at-affordable-price/','180.92.239.142','2016-12-19 12:45:29','2016-12-19 17:45:29','WOW ! What a fantastic blog.\r\nThanks',0,'0','Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 6.1) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/55.0.2883.87 Safari/537.36','',0,0),
	(25156,18,'Felix Miata','mrmazda@earthlink.net','http://fm.no-ip.com/Auth/auth','24.144.120.162','2016-12-24 01:34:14','2016-12-24 06:34:14','\"1em = 12pt = 16px = 100%\"\r\n\r\nNot any more as of several years ago, when all major browser engines adopted the CSS3 spec that equates 12pt to 12px on screen media. Only in KHTML (KDE\'s Konqueror via option) or very old and unsupported browsers does pt mean pt for screen media. Gecko does provide a proprietary workaround for pages that need a physical size specification to be available for screen media, in the form of the mozmm unit at .352775mozmm/pt. 12pt=4.23333mozmm, 10pt=3.52775mozmm, 9pt=3.174975mozmm, etc. See it in action, or not, in various browsers on e.g. http://fm.no-ip.com/Auth/dpi-screen-window.html',0,'0','Mozilla/5.0 (X11; Linux x86_64; rv:49.0) Gecko/20100101 SeaMonkey/2.46','',0,0),
	(25591,18,'Unit in CSS(font-size)(px, pt, em&amp; percent) &#8211; Site Title','','https://fwcoding.wordpress.com/2017/01/04/unit-in-cssfont-sizepx-pt-em-percent/','192.0.118.170','2017-01-04 14:25:12','2017-01-04 19:25:12','[&#8230;] https://kyleschaeffer.com/development/css-font-size-em-vs-px-vs-pt-vs/ [&#8230;]',0,'0','The Incutio XML-RPC PHP Library','pingback',0,0),
