	(101,1,'2008-10-30 10:57:10','2008-10-30 14:57:10','I wanted to really take the concept of my \"<a href=\"http://www.kyleschaeffer.com/?p=31\">Karate Corners</a>\" design to new levels, so I created this simple demo to show you how visual elegance can work in tandem with technical simplicity.<!--more-->\n\nSeeing is believing, so without further adieu...\n\n<a href=\"http://www.kyleschaeffer.com/karatecorners/\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-102\" title=\"Karate Corners Demo\" src=\"https://kyleschaeffer.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2008/10/karate-demo.jpg\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" width=\"319\" height=\"173\" /></a>\n\n<strong><a href=\"http://www.kyleschaeffer.com/karatecorners/\">View the Karate Corners Demo by clicking here.</a></strong>','Five Elegant Rounded Corner Boxes','','publish','open','open','','five-elegant-rounded-corner-boxes','','','2008-10-30 10:57:10','2008-10-30 14:57:10','',0,'http://www.kyleschaeffer.com/?p=101',0,'post','',18),
