	(400,1,'2010-01-12 00:58:06','2010-01-12 05:58:06','I updated the site\'s theme a bit to add some \"fresh.\" Please give me a bit of time to go through some of my older posts and clean them up for a better display. I\'m trying to be very good and do things like add <acronym title=\"acronym\">&lt;acronym/&gt;</acronym> tags and <code>&lt;code/&gt;</code> tags to my posts. Ooh, how very accessible of me. My SEO senses are tingling. More tutorials and other goodies coming very soon.','Did You Notice?','','publish','open','open','','did-you-notice','','','2010-01-12 00:58:06','2010-01-12 05:58:06','',0,'http://www.kyleschaeffer.com/?p=400',0,'post','',1),
